snippet.title: The Full Twisted Johnny Depp Amber Heard Story From Beginning To End
snippet.description:
To say the least, Johnny Depp and Amber Heard have had a tumultuous relationship. Despite the fact that they separated in 2016, court fights have continued as both sides have claimed domestic violence. Today, we take a look back at their relationship's timeline, as well as each of their fatal blunders.
